response.about:
The way I see it, life is a collection of experiences. Once a moment, a circumstance, a chapter in life passes, it is over. The pages do not stop turning for anything and they do not turn backwards.

That makes every moment infinitely precious. There are two ways to cherish a moment. One is to enjoy it before it passes. The other is to capture it in your heart and look back on it when it is gone.

What makes Accent Photography unique is that we are dedicated to helping our clients do both.

Our first goal is to actually enrich, not just capture our clients' experiences. Much too often, photographers lose sight of the fact that a photograph's real value lies in the memories and emotions it awakens, not in the fact that a particular photographer took it.

We want to make the time you spend with us even more enjoyable than if we had not been the ones sharing it with you. The way we see it, photography should be fun.

Our second goal is to create for each of our clients a collection that they absolutely love, a collection that will help them remember and relive the magic of their special moments again and again.

To me, that is the beauty of photography.
